title: Generational Blessings
itunes:title: Generational Blessings
description:
How you live your life each day matters. The choices you make today not only affect just you, but the ripple is felt in your family line for generations to come. As you gain a fresh perspective of generational blessings, you will be propelled to live with a new sense of wonder, anticipation and appreciation of God’s blessings in your life.Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
